1. Start a standalone keycloak server 
$ cd ./bin
$ ./standalone.sh -Djboss.socket.binding.port-offset=100 
1.1 Add a management user 
$ cd bin
$ ./add-user.sh -u admin -p 123456 -ds 
1.2 Go to wildfly server to check the container with admin/123456
http://127.0.0.1:10090
1.3 Go to keycloak server and login with any admin/admin to see keycloak app
Go to the application runtime 
http://localhost:10090/console/index.html#deployments;path=deployment~dply-keycloak-serverwar
find where keycloak is published http://127.0.0.1:8081

2. Generate certs
openssl req -newkey rsa:2048 -nodes -keyout key.pem -x509 -days 365 -out certificate.pem
or
keytool -genkey -alias localhost -keyalg RSA -keystore keycloak.jks -validity 10950
...
https://www.keycloak.org/docs/latest/server_installation/


